metadata.name: NILA
metadata.description:
Nila, who roams the realm of enigma and wonder,
collecting blue sunflowers and peacock feathers to ponder,
Her eyes, like sapphires, and her tresses, an oceanic sight,
She moves with an ethereal grace, like waves under the moonlight.

A goddess of devotion, her beauty is unparalleled.
Her smile and warmth, a precious gem to behold.
In her aura, love and peace unite.
Nila, a luminous pearl in this land of mystical might.


Paper Artist : Merisha 
Photographer : Savio
Audio : Yes
Inspiration : Yulia
